{"word":"ἐφορμίζω","slug":"ἐφορμίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐφορμίζω</b></el> <el>(attic <el>ιῶ</el>) </el>\n  <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to bring</i> a ship <i>to its moorings</i> (<el>ὅρμος</el>): — <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> and <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to come to anchor</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to seek refuge in</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}